WEBVTT

00:11:59.777 --> 00:12:02.895
is the only source
of political legitimacy.

00:12:02.919 --> 00:12:06.257
I was asked once, "The Party
wasn't voted in by election.

00:12:06.281 --> 00:12:08.487
Where is the source of legitimacy?"

00:12:08.511 --> 00:12:12.049
I said, "How about competency?"

00:12:12.073 --> 00:12:13.526
We all know the facts.

00:12:13.550 --> 00:12:15.467
In 1949, when the Party took power,

00:12:15.491 --> 00:12:18.794
China was mired in civil wars,
dismembered by foreign aggression,

00:12:18.818 --> 00:12:23.089
average life expectancy
at that time, 41 years old.

00:12:23.113 --> 00:12:25.999
Today, it's the second largest
economy in the world,

00:12:26.023 --> 00:12:28.602
an industrial powerhouse,
and its people live

00:12:28.626 --> 00:12:30.689
in increasing prosperity.